Ubuntu:
gsettings set org.gnome.nautilus.preferences always-use-location-entry true
gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences button-layout ":minimize,maximize,close"

*Arch installs*
sudo pacman -S perl-net-smtp-ssl perl-authen-sasl perl-mime-tools ctags gvim git tmux base-devel minicom xsel bat the_silver_searcher bat

*Fedora install*
sudo dnf install cmake tree git tmux tcputils ctags minicom gvim curl p7zip man-pages dtc python-pip flex bison astyle autoconf automake ncurses-devel uboot-tools
sudo dnf module install bat

